channel.title: Hah Bah Gee Scape V5 - Released Finally
channel.description:
Well, I have been extremely busy helping others code that I figured you all wanted another release from me, So I took a few days and put this together for you all as a quick term release til I finish it all and wrap it up in V6.
Features:
-Admins now have infinite specials. -Barrows is like 95% real like runescape. Use spade on hill, click coffin, they spawn, you kill, get kc, at 5 kc you tele to tunnels when you click last coffin, and then in tunnels kill npcs for kc, use doors to get to chest and open chest for random reward... -New Home -New starting outfit -Added like 2 quests -Fixed up Jad a bit gave him like 20 waves, now when you kill, it teles you out, gives message, and adds cape into inv. -Added drops to Tzhaar -99% of all items equip correctly now. -Spade for barrows can be bought in fletching shop. -Fixed experience rates, so now its more realistic and it takes time for a 99. -Took bank from edgy pking 1v1, to make banking more real.
Base: Figment (Czar)
Credits: Me: 40% Figment: 15% Reforced: 45%

If you feel credits were not given correctly, please post why and give a valid explanation. If I left something out please post it.
Please post if you download, I will not remove because that's annoying to people, but I assume with most people here you are mature enough to post if you download without me threatening.
